### SMS Service API Tests

# Base URL - change if running on different port
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5010

### Health Check - Liveness
GET {{baseUrl}}/healthz/live

### Health Check - Readiness  
GET {{baseUrl}}/healthz/ready

### Send Test SMS - Valid Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/test-sms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "+15612183303",
  "message": "Hello! This is a test SMS message from the service."
}

### Send Test SMS - Invalid Phone Number
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/test-sms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "invalid-phone",
  "message": "This should fail validation"
}

### Send Test SMS - Empty Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/test-sms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "+12362370176",
  "message": "Hello"
}

